      EIGHTH INTERNATIONAL CONFERENCE ON CONCURRENCY THEORY (CONCUR'97)
      *****************************************************************
                     
                      July 1 - 4, 1997, Warsaw, Poland

                PROGRAM, GENERAL INFORMATION AND REGISTRATION FORM
                --------------------------------------------------

You can find program, general information and registration form at CONCUR'97 
web sites:

